(2) 
                Developing long term services such as a meta reconciliation service for authority data. As the project infrastructure revolves around creating and sharing linked data datasets, providing the means for linking entities with available authority data providers is crucial. This resulted in the development of Dikudex, a unified API that allows search across multiple authority providers (e.g. GND, Geonames, Wikidata, but also local data sources such as the HOV ; 
                <https://hov.isgv.de/>
                ] or other DIKUSA projects). This service is intended to be continuously maintained and made available by KompetenzwerkD.
